WHAT ARE THE BARRIERS FOR AN EFFICIENT PROCESS?
BARRIER
EXAMPLES
Scheduling
• Estimated times in scheduling system
inaccurate
• Last minute changes disrupt flow
• Case order inhibits effciency
• Parallel rooms not scheduled optimally
Central Sterile
• Missing instruments not documented
• Pereference cards are incorrect
• Some trays must be rapidly processed, but
are not ready
Pre-Operative Area
• Variable times when patients are told to
arrive
• Last minute tests cause delays
